{"tid":352074,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"四川九寨溝發生7級地震 縣城停電建築物損毀","createTime":"2017-08-08T13:57:15.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-08T16:17:26.000Z","uid":37554,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"dffaa4e145fedebc8c56e8404aeba81c06a6631b","tid":352074,"uid":37554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T13:57:15.000Z","msg":"中國地震台網指出，今晚9時19分在四川阿壩州九寨溝縣附近，發生7級左右地震，震源深度20公里。在四川成都、陝西西安、甘肅蘭州都有民眾聲稱感到震動。<br />\n<br />\n有身處九寨溝的民眾稱地震發生後當地全縣停電、建築物牆身剝落，中國移動的信號消失，大批民眾已湧到室外暫避。<br />\n<br />\n當地政府指出，在震央方圓20公里範圍內的人口約2.1萬，50公里範圍內約6.3萬，100公里範圍內約30萬。"},{"pid":"f53c58b74c0440d9da1495d8c074fd87e3720330","tid":352074,"uid":46644,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T13:58:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"106d490cc047fcea7a1155f058a4ea5a67dc25ee","tid":352074,"uid":44454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T14:00:45.000Z","msg":"我好關心有冇人死傷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be2705487c5e7cdc13a8918896fb30b99372bb14","tid":352074,"uid":128210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T16:00:36.000Z","msg":"香港準備被捐錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n_川官員心諗，又可以換車買屋了。"},{"pid":"c426a1f828dd425a867d14555f5b5073073d989b","tid":352074,"uid":33653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T16:17:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>香港準備被捐錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n_川官員心諗，又可以換車買屋了。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n酒濃於水啊"}]}